headline: CME Group (NasdaqGS:CME) Declares US$1.25 Per Share Dividend for Second Quarter
summary: CME Group (NasdaqGS:CME) recently affirmed a second-quarter dividend of $1.25 per share, which may have added stability for investors, complementing the company's 16.53% stock price rise over the last quarter. Additionally, the company's solid financial results, with an increase in net income and earnings per share for Q1 2025, likely bolstered investor confidence. The introduction of new futures products, such as XRP and Solana futures, could appeal to crypto enthusiasts amid Bitcoin's surge...

headline: CME Group Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: CME Group Inc., the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today declared a second-quarter dividend of $1.25 per share. The dividend is payable June 25, 2025 to shareholders of record as of June 9, 2025.
